.el .ds Aq '
.TH btctax-reconcile-bulk-link-transfer 1  btctax "btctax manual"
.SH NAME
bulk\-link\-transfer \- Bulk\-confirm self\-transfers: link every PENDING outbound transfer in a time frame to one destination wallet (non\-taxable). Shows a preview + requires \-\-yes (or interactive y/N)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbulk\-link\-transfer\fR <\fB\-\-to\-wallet\fR> [\fB\-\-year\fR] [\fB\-\-from\fR] [\fB\-\-to\fR] [\fB\-\-from\-wallet\fR] [\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR] [\fB\-\-yes\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Bulk\-confirm self\-transfers: link every PENDING outbound transfer in a time frame to one destination wallet (non\-taxable). Shows a preview + requires \-\-yes (or interactive y/N)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-to\-wallet\fR \fI<TO_WALLET>\fR
Destination wallet every selected outflow links to
.TP
\fB\-\-year\fR \fI<YEAR>\fR
Restrict to a single tax year (mutually exclusive with \-\-from/\-\-to)
.TP
\fB\-\-from\fR \fI<FROM>\fR
Range start (YYYY\-MM\-DD; requires \-\-to)
.TP
\fB\-\-to\fR \fI<TO>\fR
Range end (YYYY\-MM\-DD, inclusive; requires \-\-from)
.TP
\fB\-\-from\-wallet\fR \fI<FROM_WALLET>\fR
Only outflows FROM this source wallet
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Print the preview and exit without writing
.TP
\fB\-\-yes\fR
Skip the interactive confirmation (non\-interactive apply)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
